snippet.title: Stronghold Kingdoms MMO Trailer (English)
snippet.description:
Play for Free - http://strongholdkingdoms.com/

Stronghold Kingdoms is the world's first persistent castle MMO, created by Firefly Studios. A unique free to play PC strategy game, Stronghold Kingdoms brings together online interactivity and community, with a richly depicted medieval world and thousands of real world players.

Like - http://bit.ly/shkfbook
Follow - http://bit.ly/SHKTwitter
Subscribe - http://bit.ly/fftubesub 
Play - http://strongholdkingdoms.com/
